article.description: — Loren Cristian Jackson had 19 points and nine assists as Akron easily beat Cedarville 97-49 on Saturday.
article.headline: Jackson scores 19 to lead Akron over Cedarville 97-49
article.linkText: Jackson scores 19 to lead Akron over Cedarville 97-49
article.story: AKRON, Ohio -- — Loren Cristian Jackson had 19 points and nine assists as Akron easily beat Cedarville 97-49 on Saturday. Jermaine Marshall had 12 points for Akron (1-0). Ali Ali added 12 points. Mikal Dawson had 11 points. Jay Maughmer had 13 points for the Yellow Jackets. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
